# backend_schema_map.me
# Purpose: Maps the real Supabase backend as it exists in the repository — tables,
#          triggers, RPCs, views, policies, and Edge Functions derived from actual
#          migration files and source code. This is evidence-based, not summary.
# Scope: Android v1 implementation, cross-referenced against iOS production behaviour.
#
# How this differs from existing docs:
#   data_contracts.me     — defines what clients must query; this file describes what
#                           exists on the backend including internal systems clients
#                           never call, and explains WHY each piece exists.
#   backend_authority.me  — defines rules; this file describes the actual implementation
#                           of those rules including trigger names, function signatures,
#                           known bugs, and migration history.

