### `clubs`
- **Purpose**: Core entity for every pickleball club. One row per club.
- **Android v1**: Required for all club discovery, detail, booking, and credit flows.
- **Audience**: Player-facing and owner-facing.
- **Key columns**:
  - `id UUID PK`
  - `name TEXT`
  - `description TEXT NULL`
  - `created_by UUID FK → auth.users` — club owner
  - `image_url TEXT NULL` — preset key string OR full Supabase Storage URL (custom upload wins)
  - `custom_banner_url TEXT NULL` — custom banner URL; nil = use preset
  - `hero_image_key TEXT NULL` — one of: `hero_1`–`hero_6`; maps to local asset name
  - `latitude FLOAT8 NULL` — LEGACY: prefer `club_venues` for coordinates; fallback only
  - `longitude FLOAT8 NULL` — LEGACY: same
  - `venue_name TEXT NULL` — LEGACY: prefer primary `ClubVenue.venueName`
  - `street_address TEXT NULL` — LEGACY
  - `suburb TEXT NULL` — LEGACY
  - `state TEXT NULL` — LEGACY
  - `postcode TEXT NULL` — LEGACY
  - `country TEXT NULL` — LEGACY
  - `stripe_connect_id TEXT NULL` — denormalised from `club_stripe_accounts`; used by payment intent creation
  - `subscription_tier TEXT DEFAULT 'free'` — denormalised from `club_subscriptions` via `stripe-webhook`; do not write from client
  - `avatar_background_color TEXT NULL FK → avatar_palettes(palette_key)` — NOT VALID constraint; legacy hex values may exist in old rows; new saves must use a valid palette_key
  - `timezone TEXT DEFAULT 'Australia/Perth'` — IANA timezone; set at club creation
  - `code_of_conduct TEXT NULL` — policy text; displayed and accepted by new members
  - `cancellation_policy TEXT NULL` — cancellation policy text
  - `win_condition TEXT`
  - `default_court_count INT`
  - `members_only BOOL` — when TRUE, booking into this club's games requires an approved `club_members` row; enforced server-side by `book_game` RPC and bookings INSERT RLS
- **MUST APPEAR in all 5 club select strings**: `latitude`, `longitude` (omitting silently breaks nearby discovery).
- **LEGACY note**: Club-level address fields (`venue_name`, `street_address`, `suburb`, `state`, `postcode`, `country`, `latitude`, `longitude`) were soft-deprecated at Stage 4. `club_venues` is now the authoritative location source. Android must implement the same fallback logic.

