## 9. BACKEND RISK REGISTER

| Risk | Description | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| `booking_status` enum cast | Direct string comparison raises 22P02 | Always cast to `::text` in PL/pgSQL |
| PGRST202 for new RPCs | PostgREST schema cache doesn't pick up new functions | Use PATCH/INSERT directly for `use_credits` and `issue_cancellation_credit` |
| Legacy address fields | `clubs.latitude/longitude` may be stale or missing if venue rows exist | Always check `club_venues` first; fall back to club fields |
| `confirmed_count` stale | Denormalised game count can be behind | Use live attendee query for accurate `spotsLeft` |
| FCM missing from all push Edge Functions | Android devices won't receive push notifications | Must update 5+ Edge Functions before Android v1 ships |
| `promote_top_waitlisted` trigger fires on cancel | Causes booking status changes without explicit client action | Android must poll/refresh booking state after any cancellation |
| `revert_expired_holds_and_repromote` cron | `pending_payment` can flip to `waitlisted` between poll cycles | Android must handle both transitions gracefully |
| `club_admins` recursion policy removed | Non-owner admins can only see their own admin row | Use `auth.uid() = user_id` queries; no sibling-lookup |
| `tournament` skill_level in legacy iOS model | **FIXED 2026-04-28** — `SkillLevel` enum updated, migration `20260428_normalize_skill_level_tournament.sql` normalizes DB rows | Never send `"tournament"` to DB; iOS `SkillLevel` enum now has 4 cases only: `all`, `beginner`, `intermediate`, `advanced` |
| `chat_push NULL` in old rows | `notification_preferences.chat_push` can be NULL | Treat NULL as true (opted-in) |
| `pg_net` settings required for push trigger | `app.supabase_url` and `app.supabase_anon_key` DB settings must be configured | Without these, waitlist push silently skipped (promotion still works) |
| `avatar_color_key` nullable | NULL profiles use wrong colour if default not handled | Always resolve against `midnight_navy` (is_default=TRUE) when key is NULL |
| `app_config` key missing | Nil key causes reminder scheduling to fail | Surface error to user; never silently default |
| `waitlist_position` gaps | Brief gap between compaction and new insert within same transaction | Shared `games FOR UPDATE` lock in both `book_game` and `recompact_waitlist_positions` prevents any persistent gap |

