## 11. VIOLATION IMPACT

- **Wrong UUID case in filters** → 0 rows returned; features silently broken
- **Missing `payment_method` in booking select** → all attendees shown as "Unpaid"
- **Missing `hold_expires_at` in booking select** → 400 error; attendee list shows 0 players
- **Using `use_credits` via PostgREST** → PGRST202; credits not deducted; player gets free booking
- **Using `"tournament"` as skill_level** → 22P02 on any RPC that validates the field. Valid values: `all`, `beginner`, `intermediate`, `advanced` only. Any other value must be rejected client-side before sending to DB.
- **Using `"ladder"` as game_format** → DB CHECK constraint rejects with 400. Use `"king_of_court"`.
- **Writing `"free"` or any other non-canonical value as payment_method** → DB CHECK constraint rejects with 400.
- **Labelling `curr_credits_returned_cents` as "Refunded"** → misleads users; no Stripe cash refund flow exists. The correct UI label is "Credits Returned".
- **Ignoring `club_venues`, using only legacy club address** → wrong coordinates; map navigation fails for relocated clubs
- **Not handling `pending_payment` state** → player sees wrong CTA; can't complete waitlist-promoted booking
- **Not adding FCM support to Edge Functions** → Android users receive no push; waitlist holds expire unnoticed; review prompts never delivered
- **Hardcoding plan limits (Free=3/50, Starter=20/200)** → wrong UI; paywall misrepresents what the user is buying; pre-fix values no longer match server
- **Deriving avatar colour from user ID hash** → colour mismatch across platforms; ignores user preference; banned pattern
- **Hardcoding reminder offset = 120** → reminder fires at wrong time if `app_config` value changes; other platforms stay in sync while Android drifts
- **Direct self-booking INSERT bypassing `book_game` RPC** → race condition on capacity; membership gate bypassed; non-member can book members-only games
- **Ignoring `membership_required` error from `book_game`** → app shows confusing error or crashes; user has no guidance on how to resolve the block
